      <div id="EOAS-carousel" class="ubc-carousel carousel slide" role="complementary" aria-label="promotions"> 
       <div class="carousel-inner"> 
        <div class="item active"> 
         <img src="/home/features/ESB-medium2.jpg" alt="EOAS" style="width:100%;"> 
         <div class="carousel-caption" style="padding-top:7px;"> 
          <p><b>EOAS</b> is one of the largest and most diverse departments of its kind in the world. Our research and teaching interests span the history of the Earth and the evolution of its structure from core to stratosphere. </p> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="item"> 
         <a href="http://www.mdru.ubc.ca/"><img src="/home/features/mdru.jpg" alt="MDRU" style="width:100%;"></a> 
         <div class="carousel-caption" style="padding-top:7px;"> 
          <p><b>Mineral Deposit Research Unit</b></p> 
          <p>MDRU is a collaborative venture between the mining industry and EOAS. <a href="http://www.mdru.ubc.ca/" class="ReadMoreBtn">Read More</a> </p> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="item"> 
         <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/infrastructure/pcigr.html"><img src="/home/features/nubc_42-feature.jpg" alt="PCIGR" style="width:100%;"></a> 
         <!--      <img src="/home/features/pcigr.jpg" alt="PCIGR" style="width:100%;"> --> 
         <div class="carousel-caption" style="padding-top:7px;"> 
          <p><b>Pacific Centre for Isotopic and Geochemical Research</b></p> 
          <p>The PCIGR facility specializes in high-precision radiogenic and stable isotope ratios, elemental concentrations, laser ablation and geochronology. <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/infrastructure/pcigr.html">Read More</a> </p> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="item"> 
         <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/geodisaster_cfd/index.html"><img src="/home/features/gdcfd-new.jpg" alt="GDCFD" style="width:100%;"></a> 
         <div class="carousel-caption" style="padding-top:7px;"> 
          <p><b>Geophysical Disaster Computational Fluid Dynamics Centre</b></p> 
          <p>The GDCFDC at UBC studies weather-related and other natural disasters. <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/geodisaster_cfd/index.html">Read More</a> </p> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="item"> 
         <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/infrastructure/emxdf.html"><img src="/home/features/emxdf-merge-new.jpg" alt="EMXDF" style="width:100%;"></a> 
         <div class="carousel-caption" style="padding-top:7px;"> 
          <p><b>Electron Microbeam / X-Ray Diffraction Facility</b></p> 
          <p>This Facility is an integration of three laboratories and many instruments. (electron microprobe, SEM, X-ray spectrometer, X-ray powder diffractometer...) <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/infrastructure/emxdf.html">Read More</a> </p> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="item"> 
         <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/infrastructure/cesl.html"><img src="/home/features/ceslmerge2.jpg" alt="CESL" style="width:100%;"></a> 
         <div class="carousel-caption" style="padding-top:7px;"> 
          <p><b>Centre for Experimental Study of the Lithosphere</b></p> 
          <p>The CESL laboratory supports high-temperature and high-pressure experimentation in petrology, geochemistry, structural geology and volcanology. <a href="http://www.eos.ubc.ca/research/infrastructure/cesl.html">Read More</a> </p> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
